  • Constructor Details

    • Appointment

      public Appointment(int appointmentId, String title, String description, String location, String contactName, String type, LocalDateTime startTime, LocalDateTime endTime, int customerId, int contactId, int userId)
      Constructs an Appointment object for displaying in the TableView. This constructor initializes all attributes based on database query results. The 'contactName' is retrieved through a JOIN query from the contacts table.
      Parameters:
      appointmentId - Unique identifier from the appointment table.
      title - Title from the appointment table.
      description - Description from the appointment table.
      location - Location from the appointment table.
      contactName - Contact name from the contacts table.
      type - Type from the appointment table.
      startTime - Start time, converted from timestamp in the appointment table.
      endTime - End time, converted from timestamp in the appointment table.
      customerId - Customer ID from the appointment table.
      contactId - Contact ID from the appointment table.
      userId - User ID from the appointment table.

    • Appointment

      public Appointment(int appointmentId, LocalDateTime startTime, LocalDateTime endTime)
      Constructor for creating Appointment objects that are upcoming within 15 minutes. Utilized after logging into the application to alert about imminent appointments.
      Parameters:
      appointmentId - Appointment ID from the database.
      startTime - Start time, converted from timestamp in the appointment table.
      endTime - End time, converted from timestamp in the appointment table.

    • Appointment

      public Appointment(String month, String type, int count)
      Constructor for generating month and type reports. Initializes month, type, and count for report generation.
      Parameters:
      month - Selected month for the report.
      type - Appointment type from the database.
      count - Number of appointments matching the month and type criteria.

    • Appointment

      public Appointment()
      Default constructor for creating a placeholder Appointment object. Indicates no imminent appointments on login.
